corelogic.spi.parser
Class Protocol

java.lang.Object
  corelogic.spi.parser.Protocol

public class Protocol
extends java.lang.Object

Protocol

Protocol에 의해 DataSet의 출력 데이타를 결정한다. 

 
 
 
   import coreframe.data.parser.Protocol;
   import coreframe.data.parser.ProtocolFactory;
   import coreframe.data.parser.DataSetParser;
   
   
            Protocol protocol = ProtocolFactory.getProtocol();
  
            DataSetParser dataParser = protocol.getParser();
            dataParser.setServerMode();
